## ğŸ› ï¸ Installation & Setup
1. Clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/your-username/SprintSync.git
cd SprintSync

2. Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

3.Initialize the app:
python main.py setup  # Optional command to create initial JSON files

##âŒ¨ï¸ Usage Examples

Command,Action,Access
python main.py register,Create a new account,Public
python main.py login,Authenticate session,Public
python main.py add-project,Create a new project,Admin Only
python main.py list-tasks,View all tasks in a project,User/Admin
python main.py complete-task [ID],Mark a task as done,Assigned User

ğŸ¤ Team Collaboration (Git Workflow)
We follow a strict feature-branch workflow to ensure code quality:

Branching: No direct commits to main. Branches are named feat/feature-name or fix/issue-name.

Tracking: Tasks are managed via [Insert Tool Name: e.g., Trello/Jira].

Review: All code is reviewed by at least one teammate before merging.

